## To stop the app
In the terminal, press `Ctrl + C`.

## To run it again later
Open VS Code → open terminal → type `npm start`.

---

## Recommended VS Code extensions

Install these from the Extensions panel (Ctrl+Shift+X):

- **ES7+ React/Redux/React-Native snippets** — shortcuts for writing React faster
- **Prettier - Code formatter** — auto-formats your code
- **Auto Rename Tag** — renames closing HTML tags automatically
- **Tailwind CSS IntelliSense** — useful if you add Tailwind later

